<fim_suffix>public class TripAlarmNode extends OffNormalAlarmNode implements TripAlarmType {
    public TripAlarmNode(UaNodeContext context, NodeId nodeId, QualifiedName browseName,
                         LocalizedText displayName, LocalizedText description, UInteger writeMask,
                         UInteger userWriteMask) {
        super(context, nodeId, browseName, displayName, description, writeMask, userWriteMask);
    }

    public TripAlarmNode(UaNodeContext context, NodeId nodeId, QualifiedName browseName,
                         LocalizedText displayName, LocalizedText description, UInteger writeMask,
                         UInteger userWriteMask, UByte eventNotifier) {
        super(context, nodeId, browseName, displayName, description, writeMask, userWriteMask, eventNotifier);
    }
}<fim_middle>// class below has no smell
